  19,58,"D wigi i I$at Ăebbi, ger lambiyya, ger tarwa n Adem, ger wid i Nebbwi akked NuĂȘ, ger tarwa n IbĂŽahim, akked IsĂŽail, ger wid Nenha u Nefren. Ma $ĂŽan asen issekniyen n UĂȘnin, ad $lin knan, s imeĂźĂźawen"
  19,59,"Lxwelf nnsen d asatu i iooan taĂ©allit, ddan d ccehwiyyat. Ad magren ttelfan"
  19,60,"Kkes ed wid isteĂŽoĂąen, iumnen, xeddmen ayen ilhan. Wigi, ad kecmen Loennet, ur pwadensen s wacemma"
  19,61,"Leonanat n Ăaden i IwaĂąĂąed UĂȘnin, i imdanen iS, di tbavnit. LemĂąahda S, s tidep, a ppevĂŽu"
  19,62,"Ur sellen, degs, i yir awal, siwa: \"tifrat\"! Dinna, lqut nnsen, Ă»Ă»beĂȘ, tameddit"
