  19,64,"Ur d nepĂ»ubbu, siwa ma s lameĂŽ n Mass ik. IneS i illan zdat nne$, i illan deffir nne$, akked wayen illan garasen. Mass ik ur Iteppu"
  19,65,"Mass n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen. Ihi, Ăąabed iT, ili d imezgi deg uĂąbad iS. Day tesnev win isĂąan ism iS"
  19,66,"La iqqaĂŽ umdan: \"ma mmute$, day a yi d ssuff$en d amuddir"
  19,67,"Day ur icfa ara umdan, ar t id Nxelq, zik, ur illi d acemma"
  19,68,"S Mass ik, ara ten Nefser, nitni akked cwaĂźen. Sinna, a ten Nerr ad zzin i Loahennama, $ef tgwecrar"
