  19,72,"Sinna, a Nsellek wid ipĂȘezziben. A Neoo degs, imednas, $ef tgwecrar"
  19,73,"Mara asen $ĂŽen issekniyen iberrzen nneÂŁ, qqaĂŽen wid ijehlen i wid iumnen: \"menyif sin irebbuyaĂą di temĂąict akw i lemwansa"
  19,74,"AcĂȘal isuta i Nesqucc, uqbel nnsen, ifen ten tarkunt, Ă»Ă»ifa"
  19,75,"Ini: \"ad Irnu UĂȘnin di laĂąmeĂŽ, i im$eĂŽĂŽqen, alamma walan acu i sen ippuwaĂąĂąden: d aĂąaqeb ne$ d imir. Ad Ă©ĂŽen anwa illan deg umkan adiran mavi, ay d bu lĂąaskeĂŽ uĂŽhifen mavi"
  19,76,"Ad Irnu Ăebbi nnhaya i wid ipwanhan. Ar Mass ik, leĂ»laĂȘ idumen ifen akafi, asisi"
  19,77,"Ma twalav win iugin issekniyen nneÂŁ, u inna: \"tarkunt, tarwa ad iyi ppunefkent, war ccekk"
  19,78,"AĂąni issen tabavnit, ne$ iu$ lemĂąahda s$uĂŽ UĂȘnin"
  19,79,"XaĂźi, a Naru ayen inna. Ad as Nessi$wzef nezzeh aĂąaqeb"
  19,80,"A NewĂŽet ay d inna, a d ias $uĂŽneÂŁ, d awĂȘid"
