  19,88,"Nnan: \"IsĂąa UĂȘnin, aqcic"
  19,89,Ni$ tebbwim d abeĂąĂąuq
  19,90,"Segs, qĂŽib flan igenwan, tcerreg tmurt, grurjen idurar s Ă©diĂȘ"
